               <persName ref="PRS9848Walatta"/> in 
               <bibl>
                  <ptr target="bm:Chaine1913RepPart1"/>
                  <citedRange unit="page">202</citedRange>
               </bibl>, but correctly indentified this as a malkǝʾ-hymn to 
               <persName ref="PRS3698ehetaKr"/> in 
               <bibl>
                  <ptr target="bm:Chaine1912Catalogue"/>
                  <citedRange unit="page">57</citedRange>
                  <citedRange unit="number">88</citedRange>
               </bibl>.
             </p>
